descriptions: [{"value":"Welcome to one of the most grand homes of its era in the original townsite of Iona. Its been owned by only one family and now is ready to be loved by yours. Located in the heart of Iona, and only steps from the Iona Square park, ball diamonds, walking path and tennis courts, yet still spaciously located on a large 1.21 acre lot, including a barn and irrigated pasture. The home is solidly built of brick with a recently replaced roof and features a large covered patio, huge back yard and a magnificent shop. Once inside, you'll find 2 main level bedrooms, 1.5 baths, a main floor laundry, kitchen and a TV room/Den. Downstairs are 2 more large bedrooms, a 3/4 bath and a huge family room along with plenty of storage. You'll appreciate the lower utilities of a gas forced air furnace and will love staying cool with the air conditioning. Owned by one of the most beloved families of Iona, and yours could be next..","sourceURLs":["https://www.trulia.com/p/id/iona/5157-hansen-ave-iona-id-83427--2074824311","https://www.remax.com/realestatehomesforsale/5157-e-hansen-avenue-iona-id-83427-gid900002278046.html"],"dateSeen":"2019-11-05T01:06:00.000Z"}]
